text: Marian Urdabayeva (born April 3, 1988) is a Kazakhstani judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 63 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the first round by Yang Junxia. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Kazakhstan Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games medalists in judo Category:Judoka at the 2010 Asian Games Category:Judoka at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Kazakhstan
